TITLE: Creating a Root Layout Component in One.js
DESCRIPTION: A basic layout component for One.js that uses the Slot component to render child routes, serving as the top-level wrapper for all routes in the application.
SOURCE: https://github.com/onejs/one/blob/main/apps/onestack.dev/data/docs/installation.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { Slot } from 'one'

export default function Layout() {
  return <Slot />
}
